snippet: Robinson Cano hit a three-run homer, Dustin Ackley had a solo shot and the Seattle Mariners got an effective outing from their bullpen in a 6-3 victory over the Baltimore Orioles on Saturday night....

headline.print_headline: Cano's 3-Run HR Lifts Mariners Over Orioles 6-3
headline.main: Cano's 3-Run HR Lifts Mariners Over Orioles 6-3

lead_paragraph: Robinson Cano hit a three-run homer, Dustin Ackley had a solo shot and the Seattle Mariners got an effective outing from their bullpen in a 6-3 victory over the Baltimore Orioles on Saturday night.
